*** Symfony Cheatsheet ***

Website: https://symfony.com/doc/

Installing symfony
=> composer create-project symfony/website-skeleton <project-name>

Configure web-server
=> composer require symfony/apache-pack		Install Apache recipe
=> /var/www/project/public/					the public directory

Run symfony application
=> cd <project-name>						navigate to the project folder
=> php bin/console server:run 				starts the server
=> php bin/console debug:router				get a list of all your routes
=> Start Server on http://127.0.0.1:8000

